scenes.description: Tokoyami Towa and Tsunomaki Watame performing 'Seishun Archive'.
Countdown interlude and transition to the next stage.

subtitles.original: 行かなくちゃ
subtitles.english: I gotta go.

subtitles.original: 零れ落ちて
subtitles.english: It's spilling over,

subtitles.original: 青春感じている妄想
subtitles.english: Delusions feeling the springtime of youth.

subtitles.original: 成長した姿を見せたい
subtitles.english: I want to show you how much I've grown.

subtitles.original: リハは完璧 本番はもっと
subtitles.english: Rehearsal was perfect, the real thing even more so!

subtitles.original: 全力で Hai Hai Huu!
subtitles.english: With all our might, Hai Hai Huu!

subtitles.original: 大切な思い出
subtitles.english: Precious memories,

subtitles.original: たくさんあるけどね まだ
subtitles.english: There are so many, but not yet...

subtitles.original: 感傷に浸ってる暇はない
subtitles.english: There's no time to be sentimental.

subtitles.original: 今世紀最大の夏が始まる
subtitles.english: The biggest summer of this century begins!

subtitles.original: Wow wow
subtitles.english: Wow wow

subtitles.original: 想像の果てにある高み
subtitles.english: The heights at the end of imagination.

subtitles.original: 勝ち取った景色は尊い
subtitles.english: The scenery we won is precious.

subtitles.original: 逃げるな限界の壁越えて
subtitles.english: Don't run, overcome the wall of limits.

subtitles.original: 僕らはまだチャレンジャー
subtitles.english: We are still challengers.

subtitles.original: Yeah!
subtitles.english: Yeah!

subtitles.original: 冷めた声に溺れたって
subtitles.english: Even if drowned in cold voices,

subtitles.original: 微かな望らを手繰り寄せるように
subtitles.english: As if reeling in a faint hope.

subtitles.original: 期待外れだと誰かが嘆く
subtitles.english: Someone laments it's a letdown.

subtitles.original: 痛いと痛いがいつも戦う
subtitles.english: Pain and yearning always fight.

subtitles.original: プライドだけを頼りに抗う
subtitles.english: Resisting by relying only on pride.

subtitles.original: 自分を信じたい
subtitles.english: I want to believe in myself.

subtitles.original: 努力は報われる
subtitles.english: Effort will be rewarded?

subtitles.original: 笑いたい奴は笑ってろ
subtitles.english: Let those who want to laugh, laugh.

subtitles.original: 感傷に浸ってる暇はない
subtitles.english: There's no time to be sentimental.

subtitles.original: 今世紀最大の夏が始まる
subtitles.english: The biggest summer of this century begins!

subtitles.original: Wow wow
subtitles.english: Wow wow

subtitles.original: 反響が足りないもっともっと
subtitles.english: The reaction isn't enough, more, more!

subtitles.original: 後悔はさせない
subtitles.english: I won't let you regret it.

subtitles.original: Ahhh!
subtitles.english: Ahhh!

subtitles.original: 想像の果てにある高み
subtitles.english: The heights at the end of imagination.

subtitles.original: 勝ち取った景色は尊い
subtitles.english: The scenery we won is precious.

subtitles.original: 逃げるな限界の壁越えて
subtitles.english: Don't run, overcome the wall of limits.

subtitles.original: 僕らはまだチャレンジャー
subtitles.english: We are still challengers.

subtitles.original: Yeah!
subtitles.english: Yeah!

subtitles.original: Uuu... Uuu...
subtitles.english: Uuu... Uuu...

subtitles.original: 重ねた手はぎゅっと離さずに
subtitles.english: Holding our joined hands tight, not letting go.

subtitles.original: 行くよ 行こう 夢見る空へ
subtitles.english: Let's go, let's go, to the dreaming sky.

subtitles.original: Uuu... Uuu...
subtitles.english: Uuu... Uuu...

subtitles.original: 窓越しに見上げた
subtitles.english: I looked up through the window,

subtitles.original: とても小さな空
subtitles.english: At a very small sky.

subtitles.original: ここで出会えたのは
subtitles.english: That we met here,

subtitles.original: 数えきれない奇跡
subtitles.english: Is a countless miracle.

subtitles.original: 繰り返した一歩が
subtitles.english: The repeated steps,

subtitles.original: きらめきを繋いで
subtitles.english: Connecting the sparkles,

subtitles.original: 星のような笑顔
subtitles.english: Smiles like stars,

subtitles.original: 導いた
subtitles.english: Guided us.

subtitles.original: Day by day
subtitles.english: Day by day

subtitles.original: みんなの声が力になる
subtitles.english: Everyone's voices become power.

subtitles.original: Stage by stage
subtitles.english: Stage by stage

subtitles.original: ここでそれぞれ目指すもの
subtitles.english: What each of us aims for here,

subtitles.original: それぞれ描くもの
subtitles.english: What each of us envisions,

subtitles.original: それぞれ願った夢へ
subtitles.english: To the dreams each of us wished for.

subtitles.original: 重ねた手はぎゅっと離さずに
subtitles.english: Holding our joined hands tight, not letting go.

subtitles.original: 一人ひとり違う色で描き出すときめき
subtitles.english: The excitement drawn by each of us in different colors.

subtitles.original: 振り向くことなく真っすぐに
subtitles.english: Straight ahead without looking back.

subtitles.original: 行くよ 行こう 夢見る空へ
subtitles.english: Let's go, let's go, to the dreaming sky.

subtitles.original: Uuu... Uuu...
subtitles.english: Uuu... Uuu...

subtitles.original: 笑いあったことや
subtitles.english: Things we laughed about,

subtitles.original: 尽きることない話題
subtitles.english: Topics that never run out,

subtitles.original: 思い出いっぱいなのに
subtitles.english: Even though we're full of memories...
